  <div class="pane-content">
    <span id="skip-content" tabindex="-1"></span>    <h1>Carer Support claims</h1>
  </div>

  
  </div>
<div class="panel-pane pane-node-content odd" >
  
      
  
  <div class="pane-content">
        <article id="node-841" class="node node-page view-mode-full clearfix" about="/new-zealand-health-system/claims-provider-payments-and-entitlements/carer-support-claims" typeof="sioc:Item foaf:Document">
    <header>
            <span property="dc:title" content="Carer Support claims" class="rdf-meta element-hidden"></span>      </header>
    <div class="field field-name-field-intro-text field-type-text-long field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><p class="intro-text">Carer Support is a subsidy funded by the Ministry of Health to assist the unpaid, full-time carer of a disabled person to take a break from caring for that person.</p></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even" property="content:encoded"><p>For more information on the subsidy, read <a href="https://www.health.govt.nz/system/files/documents/pages/carer-support-dle-new-v4-11-oct-2018.pdf">How to Claim Carer Support (PDF, 301&nbsp;KB)</a>.</p>

<h2>Claim form</h2>

<p>Full-time carers will&nbsp; receive a claim form:</p>

<ul>
	<li>when a new allocation of Carer Support has been made for their client or</li>
	<li>where a claim form for Carer Support has been processed and paid, and a claim form is sent out with the&nbsp;client&rsquo;s remaining Carer Support allocation.</li>
</ul>

<p>If you have not received a claim form for your new allocation or need a spare claim form please download the form&nbsp;&ndash; available in PDF and Word formats.</p>

<ul>
	<li><a href="https://www.health.govt.nz/system/files/documents/pages/1903sgm01-carer-support-claim-form-v7-web.pdf">Carer Support Claim Form (pdf, 123 KB)</a></li>
	<li><a href="https://www.health.govt.nz/system/files/documents/pages/carer_support_claim_form_-march2019.docx">Carer Support Claim Form (Word, 80 KB)</a></li>
</ul>

<p>Please note that while the form&nbsp;can be completed electronically,&nbsp;we currently require you to print and sign the form&nbsp;and post it to us using FreePost for processing.&nbsp;If you have purchased something, you <strong>must</strong> include the receipts for that purchase.</p>

<p>If you have any questions&nbsp;please contact your NASC or the Ministry of Health Contact Centre on&nbsp;<a href="tel:0800855066">0800 855 066</a>.</p>

<p>The timeframe for claims processing is 10 working days.</p>
</div></div></div>    </article>
  </div>

  
  </div>
<div class="panel-pane pane-node-links even" >
  
      
  
